rows.label: tlk4535016201_msg0001
rows.name:
Ah, just who I was hoping to see!
I've been meaning to thank you.

rows.label: tlk4535016201_msg0002
rows.name:
You set up that direct
trade route from Yeshiva
Harbor to Avaritia, right?

rows.label: tlk4535016201_msg0003
rows.name:
I'm really grateful for your efforts!
Thanks to you, it's so much easier to
get Avaritia goods around here.

rows.label: tlk4535016201_msg0004
rows.name:
We can even enjoy the taste of
Cinnopon Rolls now! They spoil so
fast, we couldn't get them in before.
